Message: Windows Disk Diagnostic detected a S.M.A.R.T. fault on disk {DiskFriendlyName} (volumes {VolumeNames}).  This disk might fail; back up your computer now. If you can't back up (for example; you have no CDs or other backup media); you should shut down your computer and restart when you have backup media available.  In the meantime; do not save any critical files to this disk.
